professor.</p></odd></c02></c01><c01 id="aspace_ref18_yee" level="series"><did><unittitle>Series 2. Writings by La Tourette</unittitle><unitdate datechar="creation">1966</unitdate><physdesc id="aspace_bb533b1c764885932ccd39bd2d644a21" label="General Physical Description note">Boxes 1-3</physdesc></did><scopecontent id="aspace_838d136143e7085cb143ed778c774a46"><head>Scope and Contents note</head><p>The bulk of the series are typed manuscript and published articles for the publication The Register. Also there are script pages for a project titled <title>Winter's Dream</title>, and two typed manuscripts, one titled <title>Live By Satellite: the Story of Satellite Television</title>, and the other untitled.</p></scopecontent><c02 id="aspace_ref20_hr8" level="file"><did><unittitle>Live By Satellite - typed manuscript</unittitle><unitdate datechar="creation">no date</unitdate><container id="aspace_2b8b5f922cec67307163d7546040d6b1" label="Mixed Materials" type="box">1</container><container id="aspace_3bb7fde4f2a4226e4e97a9d0c41d0eea" parent="aspace_2b8b5f922cec67307163d7546040d6b1" type="folder">15</container></did></c02><c02 id="aspace_ref21_cjf" level="file"><did><unittitle>Special to The Register - typed manuscript articles by La Tourette</unittitle><unitdate datechar="creation">no date</unitdate><container id="aspace_d058ba5f81c51a2bf41a28a2e70c01d2" label="Mixed Materials" type="box">1</container><container id="aspace_6bdf5c13761042f653701a6be61ae9c0" parent="aspace_d058ba5f81c51a2bf41a28a2e70c01d2" type="folder">17</container></did><odd id="aspace_f410f19c95739db87a8ee799408ab202"><head>General note</head><p>Some may correspond with published articles in The Register.</p></odd></c02><c02 id="aspace_ref23_ggh" level="file"><did><unittitle>Live By Satellite - typed manuscript</unittitle><unitdate datechar="creation">no date</unitdate><container id="aspace_745307b98f9385ea37b3b5c2de5fc791" label="Mixed Materials" type="box">2</container><container id="aspace_8483431577d