"aspace_fe0059947cb6c0d0b749553c349bb0ea"><head>Scope and Contents note</head><p>Includes business correspondence, notes and letters that appear to be from family, friends, and students, and a very small amount outgoing correspondence.</p></scopecontent><c02 id="aspace_ref33_brp" level="file"><did><unittitle>Business correspondence</unittitle><unitdate datechar="creation">1960s-1970s</unitdate><container id="aspace_cdcb964b048b544b63717abf9e593e5d" label="Mixed Materials" type="box">1</container><container id="aspace_1b8e5c43a200d3973be5a213bd6b9cd2" parent="aspace_cdcb964b048b544b63717abf9e593e5d" type="folder">5</container></did><odd id="aspace_e3d84e98970f96e74f6c3dc49b1703d7"><head>General note</head><p>Appears to be business correspondance. With Film, TV, Theater News (June 10, 1976) and flyer for Lets talk to Each Other (October 27, 1976).</p></odd></c02><c02 id="aspace_ref35_fvt" level="file"><did><unittitle>Student correspondence</unittitle><unitdate datechar="creation">1972, 1975-1976</unitdate><container id="aspace_a39e118dab2d09c1632a28751f033e88" label="Mixed Materials" type="box">1</container><container id="aspace_9344eed7e97e14236b4aba71d0903c06" parent="aspace_a39e118dab2d09c1632a28751f033e88" type="folder">6</container></did><odd id="aspace_808f8ecbf5c5b68e5722a5701ea3aee3"><head>General note</head><p>Notes that appear to be from students.</p></odd></c02><c02 id="aspace_ref37_y9k" level="file"><did><unittitle>Outgoing correspondence</unittitle><unitdate datechar="creation">no date</unitdate><container id="aspace_bdb62f2ca261c3354413d997695a24ae" label="Mixed Materials" type="box">1</container><container id="aspace_c6f2d4d0aacfe681029522fb9c67b433" parent="aspace_bdb62f2ca261c3354413d997695a24ae" type="folder">18</container></did></c02><c02 id="aspace_ref38_6s6" level="file"><did><unittitle>Personal correspondance</unittitle><unitdate datechar="creation">1963, 1966</unitdate><container id="aspace_4d5559b5c3687ce46f8227e35cde68fd" label="Mixed Materials" type="box">2</container><container id="aspace_f4728175070984ffc8a90a222eac7acb" parent="aspace_4d5559b5c3687ce46f8227e35cde68fd" type="folder">7</container></did><odd id="aspace_961d1fe5cdba3465eb14d7d5452fffb6"><head>General note</head><p>Appears to be from family and friends.</p></odd></c02></c01><c01 id="aspace_ref41_ini" level="series"><did><unittitle>Series 4. Television Projects</unittitle><unitdate datechar="creation">1955, 1966-1967, 1970-1975</unitdate><physdesc id="aspace_fb631c82506c5d31f1f4c2f848a74f9a" label="General Physical Description note">Boxes 1-3</physdesc></did><scopecontent id="aspace_fb93eb696101f1500ce81b688f1e4093"><head>Scope and Contents note</head><p>The series contains material related to television projects in which La Tourette was involved in some capacity. Included is a script for <title>Land of the Giants</title>, documents related to <title>Election 72: 18 and Over</title>, a very small number of notes and letters representing the filming of his documentary <title>Vietnam: The Village War</title>, and a nomination certificate for Best Producer from the Academy of Television Arts and Sciences.</p></scopecontent><c02 id="aspace_ref43_3f7" level="file"><did><unittitle>1974 election coverage memos</unittitle><unitdate datechar="creation">1974</unitdate><container id="aspace_a33ec57bde237f72bd02b5d50df6457d" label="Mixed Materials" type="box">1</container><container id="aspace_0971479447d9076d4cb6db214551d3c8" parent="aspace_a33ec57bde237f72bd02b5d50df6457d" type="folder">1</container></did></c02><c02 id="aspace_ref44_jd5" level="file"><did><unittitle>ABC West Coast day logs</unittitle><unitdate datechar="creation">1972-1975</unitdate><container id="aspace_fa5d64865ede5c9ac01a4cd61fe8617b" label="Mixed Materials" type="box">1</container><container id="aspace_f79e02b60551f0cc59ef238cf0250c7f" parent="aspace_fa5d64865ede5c9ac01a4cd61fe8617b" type="folder">2</container></did></c02><c02 id="aspace_ref45_jvv" level="file"><did><unittitle>E